{"tid":1738843,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"求下你唔好諗唔開","createTime":"2019-11-19T11:13:10.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-19T11:37:40.000Z","uid":335574,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"4d78c1a8a3827d48433e11909fdc6bda10c504d9","tid":1738843,"uid":335574,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T11:13:10.000Z","msg":"你之前連登開個post話要自殺<br />\n我幾經辛苦先冷靜你落嚟<br />\n之後我係tg都有同你傾計 你都冇乜嘢<br />\n有一次你仲打嚟 我哋傾得幾好 <br />\n我都聽得出你係一個好好嘅女仔 <br />\n你同我講你啲經歷 <br />\n我覺得你可以捱到而家已經好叻女 <br />\n我以為你嗰次之後已經冇事<br />\n<br />\n但係你第二次打嚟 你話你要跳樓<br />\n我聽到之後 都唔知可以講咩 <br />\n你粗口橫飛 我問你喺邊你又唔肯講 <br />\n你淨係講你喺港島區 <br />\n我聽到之後已經飛出嚟港島區搵你<br />\n雖然大海撈針但係救到嘅就一定要救<br />\n嗰晚我喺條街搵到凌晨四點 都係搵唔到<br />\n之後我已經搵唔返你 搵你你又block埋我 <br />\n其實我真係好想幫你 點解你就係唔肯畀我幫呢 <br />\n希望你而家仲有睇連登 你知道我講緊你<br />\n如果你見到呢個post 希望你真係唔好亂諗 <br />\n其實呢個世界仲有好多人關心你"},{"pid":"dc92a7ce414780045147a03823d13f73264638f0","tid":1738843,"uid":282289,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T11:15:05.000Z","msg":"希望唔係JJChan fans club<br />\n<br />\n一個都不能少<br />\n撐住<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aa8fac22785fdf09d13e964a41379334961f8a69","tid":1738843,"uid":274136,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T11:16:23.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">重啟黎明 20/11（三）500am 手足聽朝見<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0gOT6pa.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0gOT6pa.png&h=f3ea33dc&s={SIZE}\" /></span></strong></span><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KfoHZKk.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKfoHZKk.png&h=c189493c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">長期戰 不氣餒</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">兄弟爬山 各自努力</span>"},{"pid":"a4d149a91f5999a874a9dab6cb045f3a9cf98865","tid":1738843,"uid":1524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T11:17:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/a